### ==========================================================
### Habit Service — 14 requests
### Flow: create habits → complete → view stats → archive
### ==========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050
@accessToken = <paste-after-login>
@habitId = <paste-habit-guid>
@testUsername = testuser

### 1. Create habit (daily)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Morning Run",
  "icon": "🏃",
  "frequency": "daily"
}

### 2. Create habit (weekly)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Read Book",
  "icon": "📖",
  "frequency": "weekly",
  "customDays": [6, 0]
}

### 3. Create habit (custom days)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gym",
  "icon": "💪",
  "frequency": "custom",
  "customDays": [1, 3, 5]
}

### 4. List all habits
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4b. Reorder habits (exact set of active habit IDs)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/habits/order
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "habitIds": ["{{habitId}}"]
}

### 5. Get single habit
# Paste a habit ID from the create or list response
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/{{habitId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. Update habit
PUT {{baseUrl}}/habits/{{habitId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Evening Run",
  "color": "#FF5733"
}

### 7. Complete habit (today)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits/{{habitId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timezone": "Europe/Vienna"
}

### 8. Complete habit (backfill a past date)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits/{{habitId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-03-15",
  "timezone": "Europe/Vienna"
}

### 9. Undo completion
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/habits/{{habitId}}/completions/2026-03-15
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 10. Get habit stats (single)
# X-Timezone header is required — returns 400 without it
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/{{habitId}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Timezone: Europe/Vienna

### 10b. Get habit stats (batch — all active habits)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Timezone: Europe/Vienna

### 11. Get completions for a date range (inclusive, max 31 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/completions?from=2026-03-12&to=2026-03-18
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 12. Public flame page (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/public/{{testUsername}}

### 13. Public SVG flame badge (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/public/{{testUsername}}/flame.svg

### 14. Archive habit (DESTRUCTIVE — run last)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/habits/{{habitId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
